% FigS2.m  analysis of ongoing activity without locomotion and figure generation
%   Batch script to configure and run the analyses underlying Supplementary
%   Figure 2.
%
%   Outputs:
%       - A large set of analysis results saved to disk (MAT-file).
%       - A comprehensive collection of figures saved to disk.

